	"keywords": "javascript, Programming, Humor, Self Improvement, Tech",
	"description": "I had a problem. Before I tell you about this problem, be warned — you will get\nemotional if you keep reading. Your heart will break for me. There will be\nweeping, so much weeping. You will be tempted to start a GoFundMe page to help\nease my burden.\n\nOK, here it is. Ready? Grab a tissue.\n\nI have so many sneakers that I can’t remember all the pairs I own. Tragic, but\ntrue. The Red Cross has already declared this an international emergency.\n\nAlright, alright — this is not a real problem. Well, may",
