	"keywords": "javascript, Programming, Humor, Learning, Self Improvement",
	"description": "Roger opened the Medium app on his phone and looked for something interesting to\nread. He scrolled past articles about how to be more creative. He scrolled past\narticles about how to be a mega-successful entrepreneur. He scrolled past\narticles about how to write way more gooder.\n\nHe was about to bounce over to Twitter when a headline caught his eye.\n\n&gt; Forget Angular. Forget React. Introducing Tupress, the ultimate JavaScript\nframework.\nHmm, maybe it’s time to finally learn a framework, Roger th",
